{"tid":2058781,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[二大女神對決]佐佐木希定白石麻衣靚女d?","createTime":"2020-06-10T12:15:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T05:11:23.000Z","uid":141988,"like":43,"dislike":69,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"07522862a7d70cc023a28d4c68b4751f54e99c1b","tid":2058781,"uid":141988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:15:44.000Z","msg":"佐佐木希定白石麻衣靚女d?<br />\n佐佐木希<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n白石麻衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ETXE-AFYDQo/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FETXE-AFYDQo%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=a0729224&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佐佐木希 是日本模特兒，同時從事寫真偶像、演員、歌手等工作，出生於秋田縣秋田市。出道時為少女雜誌《PINKY》模特兒，現為時尚雜誌《non-no》模特兒。所屬事務所為TOP COAT。身高168公分。 維基百科<br />\n配偶： 渡部建 (結婚於 2017 年) 熱門<br />\n出生： 1988 年 2 月 8 日（32歲），日本秋田縣秋田市<br />\n身高： 1.68 公尺<br />\n<br />\n白石麻衣是日本偶像藝人、模特兒，為女子偶像團體乃木坂46成員，群馬縣出身。2011年8月，以乃木坂46一期生身分出道。曾是時尚雜誌《Ray》專屬與《LARME》常規模特兒，目前活躍於各知名時尚雜誌。白石同時是乃木坂46中擁有較多個人演藝活動、知名度較高的成員，也被認為是團體中「美」的象徵。 維基百科<br />\n出生： 1992 年 8 月 20 日（27歲），日本群馬縣沼田市<br />\n身高： 1.62 公尺"},{"pid":"4854ac6df8e0e79d92c659ec3ae83c4fc05fc8fc","tid":2058781,"uid":77092,"like":14,"dislike":15,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:18:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72be32a24604332091a45ac2921f7c6c861a9524","tid":2058781,"uid":13638,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:21:00.000Z","msg":"生狗里奈"},{"pid":"d26839f706bc1a34f727b179f26e998dff8bef82","tid":2058781,"uid":141988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4854ac6df8e0e79d92c659ec3ae83c4fc05fc8fc","tid":2058781,"uid":77092,"like":14,"dislike":15,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:18:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:21:39.000Z","msg":"白石麻衣連續4年封最美麗偶像<br />\n日本電台「文化放送」，近年都會舉行「最貌美女性偶像」選舉，近年該榜都被46系組合雄霸，昨日公布了本年度的頭20名名單，當中乃木坂46的成員就霸佔了10個位置，而已宣布了將畢業離隊，但因疫情而要延期畢業的乃木坂成員白石麻衣，今年繼續成為冠軍，她以逾4,400票連續4年成為該榜的冠軍，比起第2位的日向坂46成員加藤史帆，足足贏出千多票。<br />\n<br />\n  除白石麻衣之外，乃木坂成員鈴木絢音、齋藤飛鳥、堀未央奈、遠藤櫻均打入十大。至於48系組合則全不入十大，只得3人打入榜，包括NGT48成員加藤美南佔13位、SKE松井珠理奈佔14位，NMB山本望叶則佔15位。"},{"pid":"a5ab40054d21e9323c086f190f7b4863acb59616","tid":2058781,"uid":10300,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:21:50.000Z","msg":"佐佐木希<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n白石二奶相+亞視味"},{"pid":"bb42ef4e8c6cdec8c06833c3f1cb68988273ea25","tid":2058781,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72be32a24604332091a45ac2921f7c6c861a9524","tid":2058781,"uid":13638,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:21:00.000Z","msg":"生狗里奈"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你老婆"},{"pid":"4ab56f5bf8f59403a802a40256d99b516ece1b2b","tid":2058781,"uid":13638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb42ef4e8c6cdec8c06833c3f1cb68988273ea25","tid":2058781,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72be32a24604332091a45ac2921f7c6c861a9524","tid":2058781,"uid":13638,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:21:00.000Z","msg":"生狗里奈"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你老婆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:27:03.000Z","msg":"你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96fdd27f7323f2c8055ea0e6efdc0b4eb35d576","tid":2058781,"uid":141988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5ab40054d21e9323c086f190f7b4863acb59616","tid":2058781,"uid":10300,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:21:50.000Z","msg":"佐佐木希<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n白石二奶相+亞視味"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:27:52.000Z","msg":"但白石麻衣係日本紅過佐佐木希好多好多倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e899cc3d6f3273d266e2e938d7710eea0759c96","tid":2058781,"uid":7331,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:28:50.000Z","msg":"大原櫻子"},{"pid":"71936c0606cd7278c9bcd93f311f44c379b4e59d","tid":2058781,"uid":141988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:29:43.000Z","msg":"離隊刺激銷量 白石麻衣寫真集第28度加印<br />\n日本女團乃木坂46的27歲人氣主將白石麻衣，上月宣布將於3月底離隊後，刺激其3年前面世的寫真集《Passport》銷量反彈。出版社今日宣布第28度加印，累積出貨量40萬本。"},{"pid":"2e670cb77503b6b4d978e75bcf7030d09da035dd","tid":2058781,"uid":140570,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T14:20:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZHdKhgs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZHdKhgs.jpg&h=41dc105e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be307ce97799a2f8c2e6d55a963c2264c6072f53","tid":2058781,"uid":49163,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T14:21:07.000Z","msg":"邊個白石麻衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第一次聽"},{"pid":"38f5969715b69bf1951c7c5c13ae72161aadf933","tid":2058781,"uid":149912,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T14:22:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M0M0z3E.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM0M0z3E.gif&h=dc5a87d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n禾白屌打所有日本妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dcdef84c772eaca6fba93db2067a4bfb86dd50c","tid":2058781,"uid":207542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T14:22:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ar6DmJG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAr6DmJG.jpg&h=82d85fb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n禾白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b15db5ea257d400f8283483297e8b32b6f3f5e9a","tid":2058781,"uid":14991